description: Smallest nontrivial extension of n-th cube which is a prime.
links: Harvey P. Dale, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
mathematica: necp[n_]:=Module[{idn=IntegerDigits[n],k=1},While[!PrimeQ[ FromDigits[ Join[ idn, IntegerDigits[k]]]],k=k+2];FromDigits[Join[idn, IntegerDigits[ k]]]]; necp/@(Range[40]^3) (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Dec 11 2013 *)
author: _Patrick De Geest_
